{"pageProps":{"post":{"type_of":"article","id":645843,"title":"Creating a Modal with Tailwind & AlpineJS","description":"If you haven't tried out Alpine before, it's a minimal JS framework with Vue like syntax that can be...","readable_publish_date":"Mar 26","slug":"creating-a-modal-with-tailwind-alpinejs-2g62","path":"/jackabox/creating-a-modal-with-tailwind-alpinejs-2g62","url":"https://dev.to/jackabox/creating-a-modal-with-tailwind-alpinejs-2g62","comments_count":0,"public_reactions_count":6,"collection_id":null,"published_timestamp":"2021-03-26T00:55:56Z","positive_reactions_count":6,"cover_image":null,"social_image":"https://dev.to/social_previews/article/645843.png","canonical_url":"https://jackwhiting.co.uk/posts/creating-a-modal-with-tailwind-and-alpine/","created_at":"2021-03-26T00:55:56Z","edited_at":"2021-03-26T00:56:41Z","crossposted_at":null,"published_at":"2021-03-26T00:55:56Z","last_comment_at":"2021-03-26T00:55:56Z","reading_time_minutes":4,"tag_list":["tailwindcss","aplinejs","html","modal"],"tags":["tailwindcss","aplinejs","html","modal"],"body_html":"<p>If you haven't tried out <a href=\"https://github.com/alpinejs/alpine\">Alpine</a> before, it's a minimal JS framework with Vue like syntax that can be integrated into any website by just linking to the CDN.</p>\n\n<p>Alpine combined with Tailwind allows for rapid development of websites - so it's understandable why I'm a fan.</p>\n\n<p>In this article, we'll talk about how we can set up a modal that can be used anywhere on your site.</p>\n\n<p>If you want, you can skip to the end for the full code.</p>\n\n<h2>\n  <a name=\"setting-up-the-modal\" href=\"#setting-up-the-modal\" class=\"anchor\">\n  </a>\n  Setting up the Modal\n</h2>\n\n<p>Firstly, we need to set up somewhere to instantiate our Alpine data, for this example we'll use a <code>&lt;div&gt;</code> but it could be any element that you wish as long as it wraps the whole content.<br>\n</p>\n\n<div class=\"highlight js-code-highlight\">\n<pre class=\"highlight html\"><code><span class=\"nt\">&lt;div</span> <span class=\"na\">x-data=</span><span class=\"s\">\"{ 'showModal': false }\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n\n<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/div&gt;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<div class=\"highlight__panel js-actions-panel\">\n<div class=\"highlight__panel-action js-fullscreen-code-action\">\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"highlight-action crayons-icon highlight-action--fullscreen-on\"><title>Enter fullscreen mode</title>\n    <path d=\"M16 3h6v6h-2V5h-4V3zM2 3h6v2H4v4H2V3zm18 16v-4h2v6h-6v-2h4zM4 19h4v2H2v-6h2v4z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"highlight-action crayons-icon highlight-action--fullscreen-off\"><title>Exit fullscreen mode</title>\n    <path d=\"M18 7h4v2h-6V3h2v4zM8 9H2V7h4V3h2v6zm10 8v4h-2v-6h6v2h-4zM8 15v6H6v-4H2v-2h6z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p>Inside of that, we need to add the basic structure of a modal. This will be the full-screen overlay background as well as the white box to contain the modal content itself.</p>\n\n<p>We're also adding <code>x-show</code> to the modal so that this only shows when <code>showModal</code> is set to true in the Alpine wrapper.<br>\n</p>\n\n<div class=\"highlight js-code-highlight\">\n<pre class=\"highlight html\"><code><span class=\"nt\">&lt;div</span> <span class=\"na\">x-data=</span><span class=\"s\">\"{ 'showModal': false }\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"c\">&lt;!-- Modal --&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;div</span>\n    <span class=\"na\">class=</span><span class=\"s\">\"fixed inset-0 z-30 flex items-center justify-center overflow-auto bg-black bg-opacity-50\"</span>\n    <span class=\"na\">x-show=</span><span class=\"s\">\"showModal\"</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"c\">&lt;!-- Modal inner --&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;div</span> <span class=\"na\">class=</span><span class=\"s\">\"max-w-3xl px-6 py-4 mx-auto text-left bg-white rounded shadow-lg\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/div&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/div&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/div&gt;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<div class=\"highlight__panel js-actions-panel\">\n<div class=\"highlight__panel-action js-fullscreen-code-action\">\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"highlight-action crayons-icon highlight-action--fullscreen-on\"><title>Enter fullscreen mode</title>\n    <path d=\"M16 3h6v6h-2V5h-4V3zM2 3h6v2H4v4H2V3zm18 16v-4h2v6h-6v-2h4zM4 19h4v2H2v-6h2v4z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"highlight-action crayons-icon highlight-action--fullscreen-off\"><title>Exit fullscreen mode</title>\n    <path d=\"M18 7h4v2h-6V3h2v4zM8 9H2V7h4V3h2v6zm10 8v4h-2v-6h6v2h-4zM8 15v6H6v-4H2v-2h6z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p>Next, let's add a trigger so that we can open the modal. In this example, it's a button but it could also be any <code>a</code> tag as well.<br>\n</p>\n\n<div class=\"highlight js-code-highlight\">\n<pre class=\"highlight html\"><code><span class=\"nt\">&lt;div</span> <span class=\"na\">x-data=</span><span class=\"s\">\"{ 'showModal': false }\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"c\">&lt;!-- Trigger for Modal --&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;button</span> <span class=\"na\">type=</span><span class=\"s\">\"button\"</span> <span class=\"err\">@</span><span class=\"na\">click=</span><span class=\"s\">\"showModal = true\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>Open Modal<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/button&gt;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"c\">&lt;!-- Modal --&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;div</span>\n    <span class=\"na\">class=</span><span class=\"s\">\"fixed inset-0 z-30 flex items-center justify-center overflow-auto bg-black bg-opacity-50\"</span>\n    <span class=\"na\">x-show=</span><span class=\"s\">\"showModal\"</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n\n    ...\n\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/div&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/div&gt;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<div class=\"highlight__panel js-actions-panel\">\n<div class=\"highlight__panel-action js-fullscreen-code-action\">\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"highlight-action crayons-icon highlight-action--fullscreen-on\"><title>Enter fullscreen mode</title>\n    <path d=\"M16 3h6v6h-2V5h-4V3zM2 3h6v2H4v4H2V3zm18 16v-4h2v6h-6v-2h4zM4 19h4v2H2v-6h2v4z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"highlight-action crayons-icon highlight-action--fullscreen-off\"><title>Exit fullscreen mode</title>\n    <path d=\"M18 7h4v2h-6V3h2v4zM8 9H2V7h4V3h2v6zm10 8v4h-2v-6h6v2h-4zM8 15v6H6v-4H2v-2h6z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p>When we press the button, we will see the modal popup but we don't have any way to close it. Let's deal with that.</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>add <code>@keydown.escape</code> to the wrapper of our modal.</li>\n<li>add a <code>@click.away</code> event listener to the inner modal so that if we click outside of the white content it will also close.\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"highlight js-code-highlight\">\n<pre class=\"highlight html\"><code><span class=\"nt\">&lt;div</span>\n  <span class=\"na\">x-data=</span><span class=\"s\">\"{ 'showModal': false }\"</span>\n  <span class=\"err\">@</span><span class=\"na\">keydown.escape=</span><span class=\"s\">\"showModal = false\"</span>\n<span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n  ...\n\n  <span class=\"c\">&lt;!-- Modal --&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;div</span>\n    <span class=\"na\">class=</span><span class=\"s\">\"fixed inset-0 z-30 flex items-center justify-center overflow-auto bg-black bg-opacity-50\"</span>\n    <span class=\"na\">x-show=</span><span class=\"s\">\"showModal\"</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"c\">&lt;!-- inner modal --&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;div</span>\n        <span class=\"na\">class=</span><span class=\"s\">\"max-w-3xl px-6 py-4 mx-auto text-left bg-white rounded shadow-lg\"</span>\n        <span class=\"err\">@</span><span class=\"na\">click.away=</span><span class=\"s\">\"showModal = false\"</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/div&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/div&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/div&gt;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<div class=\"highlight__panel js-actions-panel\">\n<div class=\"highlight__panel-action js-fullscreen-code-action\">\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"highlight-action crayons-icon highlight-action--fullscreen-on\"><title>Enter fullscreen mode</title>\n    <path d=\"M16 3h6v6h-2V5h-4V3zM2 3h6v2H4v4H2V3zm18 16v-4h2v6h-6v-2h4zM4 19h4v2H2v-6h2v4z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"highlight-action crayons-icon highlight-action--fullscreen-off\"><title>Exit fullscreen mode</title>\n    <path d=\"M18 7h4v2h-6V3h2v4zM8 9H2V7h4V3h2v6zm10 8v4h-2v-6h6v2h-4zM8 15v6H6v-4H2v-2h6z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p>Next, we will set up some content for the inside. Inside of the modal, we will add a title and a close button to give the user an intuitive way to also get out of the modal.<br>\n</p>\n\n<div class=\"highlight js-code-highlight\">\n<pre class=\"highlight html\"><code>...\n\n<span class=\"c\">&lt;!-- inner modal --&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"nt\">&lt;div</span>\n  <span class=\"na\">class=</span><span class=\"s\">\"max-w-3xl px-6 py-4 mx-auto text-left bg-white rounded shadow-lg\"</span>\n  <span class=\"err\">@</span><span class=\"na\">click.away=</span><span class=\"s\">\"showModal = false\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"c\">&lt;!-- Title / Close--&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;div</span> <span class=\"na\">class=</span><span class=\"s\">\"flex items-center justify-between\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n      <span class=\"nt\">&lt;h5</span> <span class=\"na\">class=</span><span class=\"s\">\"mr-3 text-black max-w-none\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>Title<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/h5&gt;</span>\n\n      <span class=\"nt\">&lt;button</span> <span class=\"na\">type=</span><span class=\"s\">\"button\"</span> <span class=\"na\">class=</span><span class=\"s\">\"z-50 cursor-pointer\"</span> <span class=\"err\">@</span><span class=\"na\">click=</span><span class=\"s\">\"showModal = false\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n          <span class=\"nt\">&lt;svg</span> <span class=\"na\">xmlns=</span><span class=\"s\">\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"</span> <span class=\"na\">width=</span><span class=\"s\">\"24\"</span> <span class=\"na\">height=</span><span class=\"s\">\"24\"</span> <span class=\"na\">viewBox=</span><span class=\"s\">\"0 0 24 24\"</span> <span class=\"na\">fill=</span><span class=\"s\">\"none\"</span> <span class=\"na\">stroke=</span><span class=\"s\">\"currentColor\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n        <span class=\"nt\">&lt;path</span> <span class=\"na\">stroke-linecap=</span><span class=\"s\">\"round\"</span> <span class=\"na\">stroke-linejoin=</span><span class=\"s\">\"round\"</span> <span class=\"na\">stroke-width=</span><span class=\"s\">\"2\"</span> <span class=\"na\">d=</span><span class=\"s\">\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"</span> <span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n      <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/svg&gt;</span>\n      <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/button&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/div&gt;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"c\">&lt;!-- content --&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;div&gt;</span>Content goes here<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/div&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/div&gt;</span>\n\n...\n</code></pre>\n<div class=\"highlight__panel js-actions-panel\">\n<div class=\"highlight__panel-action js-fullscreen-code-action\">\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"highlight-action crayons-icon highlight-action--fullscreen-on\"><title>Enter fullscreen mode</title>\n    <path d=\"M16 3h6v6h-2V5h-4V3zM2 3h6v2H4v4H2V3zm18 16v-4h2v6h-6v-2h4zM4 19h4v2H2v-6h2v4z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"highlight-action crayons-icon highlight-action--fullscreen-off\"><title>Exit fullscreen mode</title>\n    <path d=\"M18 7h4v2h-6V3h2v4zM8 9H2V7h4V3h2v6zm10 8v4h-2v-6h6v2h-4zM8 15v6H6v-4H2v-2h6z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p>Finally, let's add some animation to the opening using Alpine's <code>transition</code> methods. On the modal itself, we'll add some Tailwind classes that smooth in the entrance of the modal. We'll also add the <code>motion-safe</code> property to ensure that we adhere to the user's preferences.<br>\n</p>\n\n<div class=\"highlight js-code-highlight\">\n<pre class=\"highlight html\"><code>  <span class=\"c\">&lt;!-- Modal --&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;div</span>\n      <span class=\"na\">class=</span><span class=\"s\">\"max-w-3xl px-6 py-4 mx-auto text-left bg-white rounded shadow-lg\"</span>\n      <span class=\"err\">@</span><span class=\"na\">click.away=</span><span class=\"s\">\"showModal = false\"</span>\n      <span class=\"na\">x-transition:enter=</span><span class=\"s\">\"motion-safe:ease-out duration-300\"</span>\n      <span class=\"na\">x-transition:enter-start=</span><span class=\"s\">\"opacity-0 scale-90\"</span>\n      <span class=\"na\">x-transition:enter-end=</span><span class=\"s\">\"opacity-100 scale-100\"</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n\n    ...\n\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/div&gt;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<div class=\"highlight__panel js-actions-panel\">\n<div class=\"highlight__panel-action js-fullscreen-code-action\">\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"highlight-action crayons-icon highlight-action--fullscreen-on\"><title>Enter fullscreen mode</title>\n    <path d=\"M16 3h6v6h-2V5h-4V3zM2 3h6v2H4v4H2V3zm18 16v-4h2v6h-6v-2h4zM4 19h4v2H2v-6h2v4z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"highlight-action crayons-icon highlight-action--fullscreen-off\"><title>Exit fullscreen mode</title>\n    <path d=\"M18 7h4v2h-6V3h2v4zM8 9H2V7h4V3h2v6zm10 8v4h-2v-6h6v2h-4zM8 15v6H6v-4H2v-2h6z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"info\">You can find out more about why we use <code>motion-safe</code> variants by reading up on this awesome article from <a href=\"https://www.smashingmagazine.com/2020/09/design-reduced-motion-sensitivities/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Smashing Magazine</a>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>Perfect, we have a modal built with Tailwind + Alpine JS.</p>\n\n<h2>\n  <a name=\"finished-code\" href=\"#finished-code\" class=\"anchor\">\n  </a>\n  Finished Code\n</h2>\n\n<p>Here is the finished code that you can copy &amp; paste into your website.<br>\n</p>\n\n<div class=\"highlight js-code-highlight\">\n<pre class=\"highlight html\"><code><span class=\"nt\">&lt;div</span>\n  <span class=\"na\">x-data=</span><span class=\"s\">\"{ 'showModal': false }\"</span>\n  <span class=\"err\">@</span><span class=\"na\">keydown.escape=</span><span class=\"s\">\"showModal = false\"</span>\n<span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"c\">&lt;!-- Trigger for Modal --&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;button</span> <span class=\"na\">type=</span><span class=\"s\">\"button\"</span> <span class=\"err\">@</span><span class=\"na\">click=</span><span class=\"s\">\"showModal = true\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>Open Modal<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/button&gt;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"c\">&lt;!-- Modal --&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;div</span>\n        <span class=\"na\">class=</span><span class=\"s\">\"fixed inset-0 z-30 flex items-center justify-center overflow-auto bg-black bg-opacity-50\"</span>\n        <span class=\"na\">x-show=</span><span class=\"s\">\"showModal\"</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n        <span class=\"c\">&lt;!-- Modal inner --&gt;</span>\n        <span class=\"nt\">&lt;div</span>\n            <span class=\"na\">class=</span><span class=\"s\">\"max-w-3xl px-6 py-4 mx-auto text-left bg-white rounded shadow-lg\"</span>\n            <span class=\"err\">@</span><span class=\"na\">click.away=</span><span class=\"s\">\"showModal = false\"</span>\n            <span class=\"na\">x-transition:enter=</span><span class=\"s\">\"motion-safe:ease-out duration-300\"</span>\n            <span class=\"na\">x-transition:enter-start=</span><span class=\"s\">\"opacity-0 scale-90\"</span>\n            <span class=\"na\">x-transition:enter-end=</span><span class=\"s\">\"opacity-100 scale-100\"</span>\n        <span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n            <span class=\"c\">&lt;!-- Title / Close--&gt;</span>\n            <span class=\"nt\">&lt;div</span> <span class=\"na\">class=</span><span class=\"s\">\"flex items-center justify-between\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n                <span class=\"nt\">&lt;h5</span> <span class=\"na\">class=</span><span class=\"s\">\"mr-3 text-black max-w-none\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>Title<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/h5&gt;</span>\n\n                <span class=\"nt\">&lt;button</span> <span class=\"na\">type=</span><span class=\"s\">\"button\"</span> <span class=\"na\">class=</span><span class=\"s\">\"z-50 cursor-pointer\"</span> <span class=\"err\">@</span><span class=\"na\">click=</span><span class=\"s\">\"showModal = false\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n                    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;svg</span> <span class=\"na\">xmlns=</span><span class=\"s\">\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"</span> <span class=\"na\">width=</span><span class=\"s\">\"24\"</span> <span class=\"na\">height=</span><span class=\"s\">\"24\"</span> <span class=\"na\">viewBox=</span><span class=\"s\">\"0 0 24 24\"</span> <span class=\"na\">fill=</span><span class=\"s\">\"none\"</span> <span class=\"na\">stroke=</span><span class=\"s\">\"currentColor\"</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n                        <span class=\"nt\">&lt;path</span> <span class=\"na\">stroke-linecap=</span><span class=\"s\">\"round\"</span> <span class=\"na\">stroke-linejoin=</span><span class=\"s\">\"round\"</span> <span class=\"na\">stroke-width=</span><span class=\"s\">\"2\"</span> <span class=\"na\">d=</span><span class=\"s\">\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"</span> <span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n                    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/svg&gt;</span>\n                <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/button&gt;</span>\n            <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/div&gt;</span>\n\n            <span class=\"c\">&lt;!-- content --&gt;</span>\n            <span class=\"nt\">&lt;div&gt;</span>Content goes here<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/div&gt;</span>\n        <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/div&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/div&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/div&gt;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<div class=\"highlight__panel js-actions-panel\">\n<div class=\"highlight__panel-action js-fullscreen-code-action\">\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"highlight-action crayons-icon highlight-action--fullscreen-on\"><title>Enter fullscreen mode</title>\n    <path d=\"M16 3h6v6h-2V5h-4V3zM2 3h6v2H4v4H2V3zm18 16v-4h2v6h-6v-2h4zM4 19h4v2H2v-6h2v4z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"highlight-action crayons-icon highlight-action--fullscreen-off\"><title>Exit fullscreen mode</title>\n    <path d=\"M18 7h4v2h-6V3h2v4zM8 9H2V7h4V3h2v6zm10 8v4h-2v-6h6v2h-4zM8 15v6H6v-4H2v-2h6z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p>If there are any errors, please reach out to me on Twitter <a href=\"https://twitter.com/jackabox\">@jackabox</a></p>\n\n","body_markdown":"If you haven't tried out [Alpine](https://github.com/alpinejs/alpine) before, it's a minimal JS framework with Vue like syntax that can be integrated into any website by just linking to the CDN.\n\nAlpine combined with Tailwind allows for rapid development of websites - so it's understandable why I'm a fan.\n\nIn this article, we'll talk about how we can set up a modal that can be used anywhere on your site.\n\nIf you want, you can skip to the end for the full code.\n\n## Setting up the Modal\n\nFirstly, we need to set up somewhere to instantiate our Alpine data, for this example we'll use a `<div>` but it could be any element that you wish as long as it wraps the whole content.\n\n```html\n<div x-data=\"{ 'showModal': false }\">\n\n</div>\n```\n\nInside of that, we need to add the basic structure of a modal. This will be the full-screen overlay background as well as the white box to contain the modal content itself.\n\nWe're also adding `x-show` to the modal so that this only shows when `showModal` is set to true in the Alpine wrapper.\n\n```html\n<div x-data=\"{ 'showModal': false }\">\n  <!-- Modal -->\n  <div\n    class=\"fixed inset-0 z-30 flex items-center justify-center overflow-auto bg-black bg-opacity-50\"\n    x-show=\"showModal\"\n  >\n    <!-- Modal inner -->\n    <div class=\"max-w-3xl px-6 py-4 mx-auto text-left bg-white rounded shadow-lg\">\n\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n```\n\nNext, let's add a trigger so that we can open the modal. In this example, it's a button but it could also be any `a` tag as well.\n\n```html\n<div x-data=\"{ 'showModal': false }\">\n\n  <!-- Trigger for Modal -->\n  <button type=\"button\" @click=\"showModal = true\">Open Modal</button>\n\n  <!-- Modal -->\n  <div\n    class=\"fixed inset-0 z-30 flex items-center justify-center overflow-auto bg-black bg-opacity-50\"\n    x-show=\"showModal\"\n  >\n\n    ...\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n```\n\nWhen we press the button, we will see the modal popup but we don't have any way to close it. Let's deal with that.\n\n  - add `@keydown.escape` to the wrapper of our modal.\n  - add a `@click.away` event listener to the inner modal so that if we click outside of the white content it will also close.\n\n```html\n<div\n  x-data=\"{ 'showModal': false }\"\n  @keydown.escape=\"showModal = false\"\n>\n  ...\n\n  <!-- Modal -->\n  <div\n    class=\"fixed inset-0 z-30 flex items-center justify-center overflow-auto bg-black bg-opacity-50\"\n    x-show=\"showModal\"\n  >\n    <!-- inner modal -->\n    <div\n        class=\"max-w-3xl px-6 py-4 mx-auto text-left bg-white rounded shadow-lg\"\n        @click.away=\"showModal = false\"\n    >\n\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n```\n\nNext, we will set up some content for the inside. Inside of the modal, we will add a title and a close button to give the user an intuitive way to also get out of the modal.\n\n```html\n...\n\n<!-- inner modal -->\n<div\n  class=\"max-w-3xl px-6 py-4 mx-auto text-left bg-white rounded shadow-lg\"\n  @click.away=\"showModal = false\"\n\n>\n  <!-- Title / Close-->\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n      <h5 class=\"mr-3 text-black max-w-none\">Title</h5>\n\n      <button type=\"button\" class=\"z-50 cursor-pointer\" @click=\"showModal = false\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n        <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\" />\n      </svg>\n      </button>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- content -->\n  <div>Content goes here</div>\n</div>\n\n...\n```\n\nFinally, let's add some animation to the opening using Alpine's `transition` methods. On the modal itself, we'll add some Tailwind classes that smooth in the entrance of the modal. We'll also add the `motion-safe` property to ensure that we adhere to the user's preferences.\n\n```html\n  <!-- Modal -->\n  <div\n      class=\"max-w-3xl px-6 py-4 mx-auto text-left bg-white rounded shadow-lg\"\n      @click.away=\"showModal = false\"\n      x-transition:enter=\"motion-safe:ease-out duration-300\"\n      x-transition:enter-start=\"opacity-0 scale-90\"\n      x-transition:enter-end=\"opacity-100 scale-100\"\n  >\n\n    ...\n\n  </div>\n```\n\n<blockquote class=\"info\">You can find out more about why we use <code>motion-safe</code> variants by reading up on this awesome article from <a href=\"https://www.smashingmagazine.com/2020/09/design-reduced-motion-sensitivities/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Smashing Magazine</a></blockquote>\n\nPerfect, we have a modal built with Tailwind + Alpine JS.\n\n## Finished Code\n\nHere is the finished code that you can copy & paste into your website.\n\n```html\n<div\n  x-data=\"{ 'showModal': false }\"\n  @keydown.escape=\"showModal = false\"\n>\n    <!-- Trigger for Modal -->\n    <button type=\"button\" @click=\"showModal = true\">Open Modal</button>\n\n    <!-- Modal -->\n    <div\n        class=\"fixed inset-0 z-30 flex items-center justify-center overflow-auto bg-black bg-opacity-50\"\n        x-show=\"showModal\"\n    >\n        <!-- Modal inner -->\n        <div\n            class=\"max-w-3xl px-6 py-4 mx-auto text-left bg-white rounded shadow-lg\"\n            @click.away=\"showModal = false\"\n            x-transition:enter=\"motion-safe:ease-out duration-300\"\n            x-transition:enter-start=\"opacity-0 scale-90\"\n            x-transition:enter-end=\"opacity-100 scale-100\"\n        >\n            <!-- Title / Close-->\n            <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n                <h5 class=\"mr-3 text-black max-w-none\">Title</h5>\n\n                <button type=\"button\" class=\"z-50 cursor-pointer\" @click=\"showModal = false\">\n                    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                        <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\" />\n                    </svg>\n                </button>\n            </div>\n\n            <!-- content -->\n            <div>Content goes here</div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n```\n\nIf there are any errors, please reach out to me on Twitter [@jackabox](https://twitter.com/jackabox)\n","user":{"name":"Jack Whiting","username":"jackabox","twitter_username":"jackabox","github_username":"jackabox","website_url":"https://jackwhiting.co.uk","profile_image":"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--1ZEi2svd--/c_fill,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_640,q_auto,w_640/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/138996/92d8c0ca-3341-4f78-90e7-5d2a17ec9da3.jpeg","profile_image_90":"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--XAjg4Krf--/c_fill,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_90,q_auto,w_90/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/138996/92d8c0ca-3341-4f78-90e7-5d2a17ec9da3.jpeg"},"readingTime":"4 min read"}},"__N_SSG":true}